  "text": "At present, ASCT is the best therapeutic option, but initially requires intensive chemotherapy to reduce the disease burden to become eligible. However, in most patients, ASCT is not feasible, mainly due to advanced age, significant comorbidities, and poor performance status, and consequently fewer than 10% of patients undergo a transplant [CITATION_1] .",
